      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>avocado<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, around the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Remove the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a spoon and slice it finely, lengthways and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
